âš ï¸ Common Mistakes

âŒ Forgetting `use` prefix
âŒ Not returning needed values
âŒ Breaking hook rules
âŒ Overcomplicating logic

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ’¡ Best Practices

âœ” Keep hooks small
âœ” One responsibility per hook
âœ” Reuse logic only
âœ” Avoid side effects without cleanup
âœ” Keep naming meaningful

